isiana politician)|Charles R. McDonald]] (born 1938) \u2013 former state representative from Morehouse and Ouachita parishes\n* [[Jack McFarland (Louisiana politician)|Jack McFarland]] (born 1969) \u2013 state representative from Winn Parish, effective 2016\n* [[Eugene McGehee]] (1928\u20132014) \u2013 state legislator; judge; from East Baton Rouge Parish\n* [[Tim McGraw]] (born 1967) \u2013 country musician; actor\n* [[John McKeithen]] (1918\u20131999) \u2013 [[Governor of Louisiana]] (1964\u201372)\n* [[W. Fox McKeithen]] (1946\u20132005) \u2013 Louisiana secretary of state (1988\u20132005)\n* [[Charles E. McKenzie]] (1896\u20131956) \u2013 U.S. representative\n* [[Baylus Benjamin McKinney]] (1886\u20131952) \u2013 Christian singer-songwriter\n* [[Joe McKnight]] (born 1988) \u2013 [[Halfback (American football)|tailback]] for the [[New York Jets]]\n* [[James M. McLemore]] (1907\u20131997) \u2013 politician; businessman\n* [[Royce L. McMahen]] (1923\u20131999) \u2013 veterinarian; sheriff of Webster Parish (1980\u201396)\n* [[A. J. McNamara]] (1936\u20132014) \u2013 state representative; U.S. District Judge from Jefferson Parish \n* [[Tom McVea]] (born 1945) \u2013 [[Louisiana State Legislature|state representative]]\n* [[Gil Meche]] (born 1978) \u2013 [[Major League Baseball|MLB]] pitcher\n* [[D. L. Menard]] (born 1932) \u2013 [[Cajun music]]ian from [[Erath, Louisiana|Erath]]\n* [[Adah Isaacs Menken]] (1835\u20131868) \u2013 actress\n* [[Myrtis Methvin|DeWitt T. Methvin Jr.]] (1924\u20132005) \u2013 Alexandria attorney\n* [[Mildred Methvin]] (born 1952) \u2013 judge\n* [[Myrtis Methvin]] (1895\u20131977) \u2013 mayor of [[Castor, Louisiana|Castor]] in Bienville Parish (1933\u201345); second woman mayor in the state of Louisiana\n* [[Emile Meyer]] (1910\u20131987) \u2013 actor\n* [[Michael J. Michot]] (born 1963) \u2013 businessman; [[state senator]] from [[Lafayette, Louisiana|Lafayette]] (since 2000)\n* [[Quintin Mikell]] (born 1980) \u2013 [[Safety (American fo