riot]] (born 1954) \u2013 politician\n* [[Ryan Theriot]] (born 1979) \u2013 [[infielder]] for the [[San Francisco Giants]]\n* [[Gerald Theunissen]] (born 1933) \u2013 banker; politician\n* [[Major Thibaut]] (born 1977) \u2013 politician\n* [[Richard Keith (Keith Thibodeaux)|Keith Thibodeaux]] (born 1950) \u2013 actor\n* [[Ledricka Thierry]] (born 1978) \u2013 politician\n* [[Dallas Thomas]] (born 1989) \u2013 [[offensive tackle]] for the [[Miami Dolphins]]\n* [[Mike Thomas (wide receiver, born 1987)|Mike Thomas]] (born 1987) \u2013 [[wide receiver]] for the [[Jacksonville Jaguars]]\n* [[Tyrus Thomas]] (born 1986) \u2013 [[power forward (basketball)|power forward]] for the [[Charlotte Bobcats]]\n* [[Addison Roswell Thompson]] (1911\u20131976) \u2013 segregationist politician\n* [[C.W. Thompson]] (1890\u20131951) \u2013 politician\n* [[Jeff R. Thompson]] (born 1965) \u2013 politician\n* [[Ken Thompson]] (born 1943) \u2013 pioneer of [[computer science]]\n* [[Lizzie P. Thompson]] (1894\u20131973) \u2013 [[state legislature (United States)|state representative]]\n* [[Richard S. Thompson]] (1916\u20131997) \u2013 [[Louisiana State Legislature|state representative]] from [[Grant Parish, Louisiana|Grant Parish]]\n* [[Sandra Thompson (politician)|Sandra Thompson]] (born 1946) \u2013 politician; environmentalist\n* [[Steve Thompson (Louisiana politician)|Steve D. Thompson]] (born 1935) \u2013 member of the Louisiana State Senate from Franklin Parish (1988\u201396)\n* [[T. Ashton Thompson]] (1916\u20131965) \u2013 [[U.S. representative]]\n* [[Dale Thorn]] (1943\u20132014) \u2013 journalist; [[Louisiana State University]] professor; press secretary to Governor [[Edwin Edwards]]\n* [[Tom Thornhill]] (born 1952) \u2013 attorney; [[State legislature (United States)|state representative]]\n* [[Marcus Thornton (basketball, born 1987)|Marcus Thornton]] (born 1987) \u2013 [[shooting guard]] for the [[New Orleans Hornets]]\n* [[George H. Tichenor]] (1837\u20131923) \u2013 surgeon; pio