int.com/news/india/coronavirus-schools-colleges-malls-movie-theatres-to-be-closed-in-telangana-until-31-march-11584186142495.html|title=Coronavirus: Schools, movie theatres to be closed in Telangana until 31 March|date=14 March 2020|website=Livemint|language=en|access-date=17 March 2020}}</ref> [[Ministry of Culture (India)|Ministry of Culture]] shut down all monuments and museums under [[Archaeological Survey of India]] till 31 March.<ref>{{Cite news|last=|first=|url=https://www.outlookindia.com/newsscroll/all-asiprotected-monuments-central-museums-across-india-to-be-shut-till-march-31-govt/1763377|title=All ASI-protected monuments, central museums across India to be shut till March 31: Govt|date=|work=Outlook|access-date=|url-status=live}}</ref>\n* '''On 17 March''', schools, colleges and multiplexes in [[Uttar Pradesh]] were shut down till 2 April and on-going examinations were postponed.<ref>{{cite web |title=All schools, colleges, cinema halls in UP closed till April 2 amid coronavirus pandemic| url=https://www.indiatvnews.com/news/india/schools-colleges-cinema-halls-in-uttar-pradesh-closed-till-april-2-amid-coronavirus-pandemic-598922|website=indianews|author=| date=17 March 2020}}</ref> [[Brihanmumbai Municipal Corporation|BMC]] ordered private firms in [[Mumbai]] to function \"only at 50% of their staff capacity or face action under section 188 of the [[Indian Penal Code|IPC]]\".<ref>{{Cite news|last=|first=|url=https://m.economictimes.com/news/politics-and-nation/bmc-orders-private-firms-to-work-only-at-50-of-their-capacity/articleshow/74661516.cms|title=BMC orders private companies to work only at 50% of capacity as coronavirus count rises|date=|work=Economic Times|access-date=|url-status=live}}</ref> [[Rajasthan]] government banned the gathering of more than 50 people in public places till 31 March.<ref>{{cite web |title=Coronavirus outbreak: Rajasthan bans all 50-plus gathering in public places till March 31, says official| url=https://www.financialexpre